profile:
//Welcome to Personal Movers - a professional moving company based in Calgary, AB.//

If you are looking for Calgary movers to relocate your business or need to move your family from Calgary, AB to any adjacent province in Canada then look no further as we have required experience and resources to take care of your move at any time of the year.

As a full service moving company we offer local, long distance, residential and commercial moving services. We also provide Delivery services and Junk Removal.

Our company employs highly qualified and experienced workers so that we can provide you with the best service we can. We strive to make your moving day a stress free experience.

AREAS SERVED: Calgary, Airdrie, Okotoks, Chestermere, Cochrane, Banff, Canmore, Red Deer, and all cities in Alberta and adjacent provinces.
services: Residential moving, Office moving, Commercial moving, Long distance moves, Junk removal, Packing/unpacking service.
specialities: Furniture assembly/disassembly, Piano moving, Oversized items moving (trucks equipped with tailgates), Heavy safes moving.
payment_method: Cash, Bank Transfer, Business Cheque, Visa, Master Card, AMEX
project_rate: Hourly; Flat rate for long distance moves;

profile: Alberta Pro Movers is a leading moving company in Calgary, and our movers have more than 31 years experience on the market of relocation services. As Calgary Movers we are a full service Calgary Moving Company including packing, transportation, loading, unloading, unpacking and Calgary storage facilities if needed. Our trucks are fully insured and you can rest assured that our movers are professionals who take care in their work. We also provide Free use of Wardrobe boxes on local moves.
services: Full service moving and storage services. We offer Frog Boxes for rent.
